        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在第二个示例中，输出中的树如下图所示：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<img src=\"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/06hepyce.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"note-img\" />{:height 236, :width 414}",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "该树是一棵冬青树。例如，对于顶点对 $(2, 4)$，从 $2$ 到 $4$ 的简单路径经过顶点 $2 \\rightarrow 1 \\rightarrow 4$，这些编号按位异或为：",
              "depth": 1
