    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>理解题意</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>直观</strong>：肯定是构造两个相邻点之间的边，也就是说，我们的任务是找两个相邻的点。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>深层</strong>：树上异或，能想到通过<strong>LCA</strong>与<strong>前缀异或</strong>（<strong>异或消去律</strong>）来进行一波操作。 ((69382d2f-3f0d-41ba-b6b2-86ea03917622))",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>树上路径异或</strong>中，$XorDist(u, v) = D[u] \\oplus D[v]$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "而本题为<strong>树上点权异或</strong>，$D[u] \\oplus D[v]$ 对应本题的 $A_{1,u} \\oplus A_{1,v}$，得到的是路径 $u \\to v$ 上<strong>除了 LCA 以外</strong>的所有点的异或和。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "那么这里我们推出以下公式：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ XorDist(u, v) = D[u] \\oplus D[v] \\oplus LCA(u, v)$$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "其中 $D[x]$ 表示从<strong>根节点</strong>到节点 $x$ 的点权<strong>异或前缀和</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "没错，跟 $u,v$ 的 $lca$ 有关系，因为这个式子中 $lca$ 出现了 3 次，没被最终消掉。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "那么我们得到<code>lca = a[1][u] ^ a[1][v] ^ a[u][v]</code>，这样我们可以记录 <strong>x 节点的子树节点们</strong>，然后<strong>按子树大小升序排序</strong>，把子树大小小的优先连上边，这样就能构造出整个树了。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>难点</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "推出<strong>异或</strong>公式，发现跟<strong>LCA</strong>有关。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>思维钩子</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>树上异或</strong>，得想到跟<strong>LCA</strong>与<strong>前缀异或</strong>的相关性。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "ll a[N][N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, i, n)cin >> a[i][j];\n\tvar sons = vector<HashSet<int>>(n + 1); // 存 i 的整个子树\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, i + 1, n) {\n\t\tll lca = a[1][i] ^ a[1][j] ^ a[i][j]; // 这个式子得到 lca\n\t\tif (lca == i)sons[i].insert(j);\n\t\telse if (lca == j)sons[j].insert(i);\n\t}\n\n\tvar ans = vector<pii>();\n\tvar p = vector<int>(n + 1); // 处理队列\n\tfa(i, 1, n)p[i] = i;\n\n\t// 按子树大小升序排序\n\tsort(all1(p), [&](const var& a, const var& b)->bool {\n\t\treturn sons[a].size() < sons[b].size();\n\t\t});\n\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint id = p[i];\n\t\tfor (int to : sons[id]) {\n\t\t\tans.pb({ id, to });\n\t\t\t// 把别的包含 to 点的删掉\n\t\t\tfa(j, 1, n)if (j != id) {\n\t\t\t\tif (sons[j].count(to))sons[j].erase(to);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tfor (const var& [x, y] : ans)cout << x << ' ' << y << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
